<item>
            <title>[LU-9346] replay-single: replay of PFL file open failure</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9346</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for bobijam &amp;lt;bobijam.xu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please provide additional information about the failure here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f2d00afc-204a-11e7-9073-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f2d00afc-204a-11e7-9073-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;During replay of PFL file open, lod_qos_parse_config()-&amp;gt;lod_use_defined_striping() initialed stripe LU-objects, but it keeps the component&apos;s LCME_FL_INIT flag; and later in lod_striping_create() these component will be skipped create OST objects, that fails the replay, it should replay creating its OST objects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
